all of them just sitting there.

987
01:32:27,266 --> 01:32:28,308
What do they say?

988
01:32:30,519 --> 01:32:31,770
Nothing.

989
01:32:31,937 --> 01:32:33,605
No talk?
None.

990
01:32:33,773 --> 01:32:37,400
Just...
They don't have anything to say.

991
01:32:38,027 --> 01:32:40,445
See, we just look at each other.

992
01:32:40,905 --> 01:32:45,742
They look at me.
And that's it, that's the dream.

993
01:32:48,079 --> 01:32:50,497
I have one where I'm drowning.

994
01:32:50,790 --> 01:32:54,334
And I gotta wake myself up and
start breathing, or I'll die in my sleep.

995
01:32:56,545 --> 01:32:57,921
You know what that's about?

996
01:32:58,422 --> 01:33:01,132
Yeah. Having enough time.

997
01:33:02,677 --> 01:33:07,889
Enough time to do what you wanna do?
That's right.

998
01:33:09,850 --> 01:33:13,478
You doing it now?
No, not yet.

999
01:33:18,359 --> 01:33:20,652
You know, we're sitting here...

1000
01:33:21,696 --> 01:33:23,822
...you and I,
like a couple of regular fellows.

1001
01:33:23,989 --> 01:33:26,700
You do what you do,
and I do what I gotta do.

1002
01:33:28,994 --> 01:33:31,996
And now that we've been face to face...

1003
01:33:34,291 --> 01:33:39,295
...if I'm there and I gotta put you away,
I won't like it.

1004
01:33:39,672 --> 01:33:40,797
But I'll tell you...

1005
01:33:43,342 --> 01:33:46,845
...if it's between you
and some poor bastard...

1006
01:33:47,012 --> 01:33:49,514
...whose wife you're gonna
turn into a widow...

1007
01:33:50,349 --> 01:33:54,686
...brother, you are going down.

1008
01:34:06,407 --> 01:34:09,242
There's a flip side to that coin.

1009
01:34:11,036 --> 01:34:15,373
What if you do got me boxed in
and I gotta put you down?

1010
01:34:16,667 --> 01:34:21,379
Because no matter what,
you will not get in my way.

1011
01:34:22,089 --> 01:34:25,008
We've been face to face, yeah...

1012
01:34:27,636 --> 01:34:31,723
