02:00:37,413 --> 02:00:40,790
Eight, 10 hours for him to set up a new out.
After that, he's gone.

1263
02:00:40,958 --> 02:00:42,917
Bye-bye. Bam.

1264
02:01:14,658 --> 02:01:16,368
(BOTH GRUNTING)

1265
02:01:35,763 --> 02:01:40,183
